<table bgcolor="#000000" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td width="10"><img width="10" height="1" src="images/space.gif" alt=""></td><td width="100%"><!-- spacer -->

<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bgcolor="#000000"  width="100%" align="center"><tr><td>
<table cellpadding="4" cellspacing="1" border="0"  width="100%">
<tr>
	<td bgcolor="#303070" width="175" valign="top" nowrap>
	<a name="post491"></a>
	
	<font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" ><b>Bludge</b></font><br>
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" >Member</font><br>
	<p>
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" >Registered: Mar 2002<br>
<!--	Location: <br>
	Posts: 76-->
</font></td>
	
	<td bgcolor="#303070" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" ><img src="images/icons/icon1.gif" border="0" alt=""> <b></b></font>
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >So, when I went about deciding how to set up my /hitsmode, I decided that I wanted to keep as much as possible in the lower quarter of the screen. <br />
<br />
<b>I play in 1024 resolution</b>.  This won’t really work in any other resolution, so you’ll have to fiddle with it on your own. <br />
<br />
<b>Me/my/others</b> - I wanted to see my hits, my being hit and others hits  <br />
<br />
<b>M2-M5</b> - I wanted names and dmg type for all three windows <br />
<br />
<b>X/Y</b> - I wanted the three new windows to sit right on top of my chat window.  Since my chat window wasn’t going to be as congested, I decided to shrink it down by a few lines. <br />
<br />
<b>Lines</b> - I wanted to have at least 5 lines of text in my combat windows<br />
<br />
<b>Font</b> - I wanted a readable font in the new windows. I was still not happy with the results, but couldn’t find a way to make the font larger.<br />
<br />
<b>Head</b> - I did not want a header at the top of each window.  It takes about 1 second to figure out which is which and once you know it, you know it forever. The headers are really silly if you ask me.<br />
<br />
<b>BG</b> I wanted a background to help me see the information. Some people don’t like it. It’s the default /transparant polygon set up that you can toggle in game for your other windows.<br />
<br />
<b>width</b> – I wanted to have My hits and My hits taken to be a smaller window.  The reason being is that both of these windows will have only one name. That of the NPC hitting you/being hit by you.  The Others window is the one where you’ll see “An orc punches Ikikikikibobob for 3 points of damage”  I wanted more room for the longer lines that would come with a two name text line, so I made it bigger than the first two. <br />
<br />
<b>Persistance</b> – Since the guide above was written, you can now add a 1 at the very end of the line to make the windows stay up all the time.  I haven’t decided for certain if I want them or not. For now, they’re always up. It is definitely a help when you are setting this up to have the 1 at the end of the line because it helps you see what you’re doing. <br />
<br />
So, what I came up with was <br />
<br />
/hitsmode my m3 143 595 6 3 0 1 195 1<br />
/hitsmode me m3 342 595 6 3 0 1 195 1<br />
/hitsmode other m3 541 595 6 3 0 1 217 1<br />
<br />
You can put it on a social hotkey if you like and then swap it around with other configurations while you are in game.<br />
<br />
Now, I had to fit my other windows around that.  I like things to be orderly, so I tried to find a set up that would keep everything in the lower portion of the screen.  I had a little leftover room, so I built a little buffer around my hp box just for grins.<br />
Anyway, you could drop the pertinent portions of my .ini file into yours if you want to see it.  Make a copy of your original .ini and if my version sucks, you can just swap it back.<br />
<br />
So, basically delete the following two sections from your .ini file and replace them with mine.<br />
<br />
[Windows1024]<br />
PlayerWinY=573<br />
PlayerWinX=778<br />
PlayerWinH=70<br />
PlayerWinW=95<br />
PartyWinY=653<br />
PartyWinX=768<br />
PartyWinH=110<br />
PartyWinW=115<br />
TargetWinY=527<br />
TargetWinX=768<br />
TargetWinH=34<br />
TargetWinW=115<br />
HotButtonWinY=527<br />
HotButtonWinX=6<br />
HotButtonWinH=236<br />
HotButtonWinW=92<br />
SpellsWinY=527<br />
SpellsWinX=98<br />
SpellsWinH=216<br />
SpellsWinW=40<br />
ChatWinY=606<br />
ChatWinX=139<br />
ChatWinH=157<br />
ChatWinW=629<br />
AffectWinY=527<br />
AffectWinX=884<br />
AffectWinH=237<br />
AffectWinW=134<br />
MainMenuWinY=550<br />
MainMenuWinX=900<br />
MainMenuWinH=200<br />
MainMenuWinW=120<br />
ItemDataWinY=309<br />
ItemDataWinX=312<br />
ItemDataWinH=150<br />
ItemDataWinW=400<br />
InventoryWinY=69<br />
InventoryWinX=388<br />
InventoryWinH=400<br />
InventoryWinW=340<br />
AltAdvWinY=20<br />
AltAdvWinX=190<br />
BazaarMerchantWinY=20<br />
BazaarMerchantWinX=190<br />
TrackWinY=10<br />
TrackWinX=140<br />
TrackWinH=324<br />
TrackWinW=120<br />
<br />
<br />
[HitsMode]<br />
MyHitsMode=3<br />
MyHitsAlwaysDraw=1<br />
MyHitsX=143<br />
MyHitsY=591<br />
MyHitsCount=6<br />
MyHitsFontSize=1<br />
MyHitsShowHeader=0<br />
MyHitsShowBG=1<br />
MyHitsBGWidth=195<br />
OtherHitsMeMode=3<br />
OtherHitsMeAlwaysDraw=1<br />
OtherHitsMeX=342<br />
OtherHitsMeY=591<br />
OtherHitsMeCount=6<br />
OtherHitsMeFontSize=1<br />
OtherHitsMeShowHeader=0<br />
OtherHitsMeShowBG=1<br />
OtherHitsMeBGWidth=195<br />
OtherHitsOtherMode=3<br />
OtherHitsOtherAlwaysDraw=1<br />
OtherHitsOtherX=541<br />
OtherHitsOtherY=591<br />
OtherHitsOtherCount=6<br />
OtherHitsOtherFontSize=0<br />
OtherHitsOtherShowHeader=0<br />
OtherHitsOtherShowBG=1<br />
OtherHitsOtherBGWidth=227</font></p>
	
